	Released 1.0.rc26.
	[bd080976b96b]

	* src/auth/auth-request.c:
	Fixed a crash when non-plaintext mechanism used auth_cache.
	[67bd670c4c1c]

	* src/login-common/sasl-server.c:
	After calling sasl_callback() the client may be destroyed already.
	Don't try to modify it.
	[5db849212114]

