	Allow creating mailbox names with '*' and '%' characters. They don't
	break anything anyway.
	[d7d87f1de71d]

2006-02-14  Timo Sirainen  <tss@iki.fi>

	* src/auth/mech-ntlm.c, src/auth/mech-rpa.c, src/imap/imap-sort.c, src
