	Don't rewrite index file every time with mmap_disable=yes.
	[5d090d03f2b5]

	* src/lib/strfuncs.c:
	t_strarray_join() was broken with input longer than 63 bytes (good
	thing we didn't use it in any important places). Patch by Johan
	Kiviniemi.
	[ae629e747baf]

