	Recent flag handling cleanups. Added some comments.
	[3b820e59610e]

	* src/imap/imap-sort.c:
	SORT might have crashed just before finishing.
	[c913cf1dfb08]

	* src/imap/imap-sort.c, src/imap/imap-thread.c, src/lib-storage/index
