	[e7166e2f8b9b]

	* src/lib-storage/index/mbox/mbox-storage.c:
	Don't crash when closing streamed mbox.
	[3957eece913f]

	* src/imap/cmd-append.c, src/imap/cmd-copy.c, src/imap/cmd-select.c,
