	to use flock() to lock indexes.
	[12b503fbb8af]

	* src/pop3/client.c, src/pop3/client.h, src/pop3/commands.c:
	Use only a single transaction for the whole duration of pop3
	session. Avoids constant locking/unlocking the indexes.
	[8c5bcd6585a4]

