2003-01-23  Timo Sirainen  <tss@iki.fi>

	* src/lib-storage/index/index-fetch.c:
	Removed the OE workaround, it still didn't work if the EXISTS/RECENT
	was sent after FETCH.
	[3b5ad60473be]

	* src/auth/auth-digest-md5.c:
	added const
	[b26b83f30f65]

